description:
Hi guys! I can’t tell you how thrilled I am that 10 million of you have now downloaded my app. A massive thanks to all of you! 

If you haven’t subscribed yet, make sure you check out my taster pack – it’s updated with 10 new beautiful step-by-step recipes every second Wednesday of the month to give you a real feel of what the app is all about. When you subscribe, you’ll get a huge selection of more than 400 exclusive recipes, all with step-by-step photography to make them super clear and easy to follow. Plus, we’re adding more recipes every month to keep you inspired and to help you learn new, amazing skills that’ll get you cooking incredible food. 

There’s a huge selection of recipes, from classic comfort food and beautiful baking recipes to festive treats, super-quick suppers and a whole lot more – there really is something for everyone.

I've also included a clever shopping list to make life a bit easier – it sorts ingredients by supermarket aisle and lets you cross off items as you shop. PLUS you can check out over 2 hours of HD video to help you master the tougher techniques as well as to get some great cooking tips and tricks. 

I hope you like it and happy cooking! 

Big love 
Jamie xxx


► Subscription to Jamie’s Recipes

Subscribe to access the largest ever collection of exclusive step-by-step Jamie Oliver recipes created exclusively for the iPhone and iPad. Updated on the second Wednesday of each month with 10 new and exclusive recipes.

Users of the free app will have access to the free taster pack, updated each month, to give you a flavor of the recipes available in the collection.

You will need an active subscription in order to access the whole collection.

► Renewing and Cancellation 

Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. This subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. The cost of the renewal will match the initial subscription price. Your auto-renew subscription can be managed or turned off by going to your Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during your active subscription period. If your subscription expires, you will only be able to access the free taster pack – you will need to purchase a new subscription to access all other content.
